# binance-futures-bot

**CLI-based Binance USDT-M Futures Bot (Mandatory Part)**

This repository contains:

- `src/market_orders.py` → Market order script (simulated)
- `src/limit_orders.py` → Limit order script (simulated)
- `bot.log` → Logs all actions and errors
- `README.md` → Setup & usage instructions
- `report.pdf` → Add manually (screenshots + explanation)

---

## Project Structure

binance-futures-bot/
├── src/
│ ├── market_orders.py
│ └── limit_orders.py
├── bot.log
├── README.md
└── report.pdf








